{"tid":60133,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[衰多口] 香香自爆十五歲失身","createTime":"2016-12-30T08:09:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T18:14:12.000Z","uid":38976,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dad79ffb486167dfe6febf3ccba665762ee79a29","tid":60133,"uid":38976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:09:02.000Z","msg":"香香(新聞 - 網站 - 圖片)昨日首次以「人妻」身份出席《愛有明天推廣預防愛滋病》活動，呼籲大家小心預防愛滋病。她說讀書時老師都有教性教育，對性有基本認識。問她何時失身﹖她起初尷尬不敢講，後來才說是15歲。追問她在那種情況下發生﹖她說在外國讀書時與三名同班的男同學在宿舍內喝酒。此時其新婚丈夫趕忙拉她離開，不讓她講下去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmetDoWcrNhkgAFHvsjoZJwaRiT8DGEqjUy2dwKxoX3rnS?filename=kXDeM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkXDeM.gif&h=c181b31f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmetDoWcrNhkgAFHvsjoZJwaRiT8DGEqjUy2dwKxoX3rnS?filename=kXDeM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkXDeM.gif&h=c181b31f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f04074fbd793ba790a2b48db82673255b94e3f2d","tid":60133,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:09:36.000Z","msg":"15<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f718af299e0f66d1209d14b6c18c6128d8214a","tid":60133,"uid":35193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:11:02.000Z","msg":"4p<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944c9ab338a4f0eed348129aecee3cabf8804fc6","tid":60133,"uid":63555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:11:35.000Z","msg":"唔係處女黨黨員咩"},{"pid":"335bd1308aa7b71bbf8b16cf5ccb4d0f46ac1b8e","tid":60133,"uid":50208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:11:44.000Z","msg":"唔係點教人預防愛滋"},{"pid":"556a13e4c54e1c5dc61fcb3d6252ac6ae1bc938b","tid":60133,"uid":66566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:12:07.000Z","msg":"三名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas